videos.description: Deebo Samuel runs 90 yards into the end zone on a kickoff from Ole Miss to put the Gamecocks on the board early.
videos.headline: South Carolina strikes early with kick return TD

videos.description: Ty'Son Williams squeezes into the end zone for a 2-yard Gamecocks touchdown.
videos.headline: Williams increases lead with 2-yd TD

videos.description: Scottie Phillips keeps Ole Miss in the game with a 9-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Ole Miss closes the gap with 9-yd TD

videos.description: South Carolina's Jake Bentley goes deep to Bryan Edwards, who makes a tough catch around a defender for a 75-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Edwards reaches around defender to haul in 75-yard  TD catch

videos.description: Ole Miss' Scottie Phillips pushes into the end zone to tie the game with South Carolina at 27.
videos.headline: Ole Miss ties game with 1-yd TD

videos.headline: South Carolina regains lead with 5-yd TD

videos.description: Scottie Phillips runs around the defense for a 2-yard Ole Miss touchdown.
videos.headline: Ole Miss answers with 2-yd TD

videos.description: Isaiah Woullard finds an opening for a 1-yard touchdown to give Ole Miss a comfortable lead over South Carolina.
videos.headline: Ole Miss continues to cruise with 1-yd TD

videos.description: A.J. Turner cuts the deficit to 3 with a 3-yard touchdown run in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: South Carolina jumps right back in it with 3-yd TD

videos.headline: South Carolina surges into lead on QB sneak
